    "connections": "Keithley 0  (Power Supply)\n    CH1 \"VCC 3.3V\" \u2192 3.3 V, 1.0 A limit\n    CH2 \"CH2\" \u2192 0.0 V, 0.0 A limit\n    CH3 \"CH3\" \u2192 0.0 V, 0.0 A limit\nHittite 0 CLKIN  (Signal Generator) \u2192 CLKIN\nFieldFox 0 CLKOUT  (Spectrum Analyzer) \u2190 CLKOUT\nKeithley 1  (Power Supply)\n    CH1 \"Beam\" \u2192 0.0 V, 1.0 A limit\n    CH2 \"CH2\" \u2192 0.0 V, 1.0 A limit\n    CH3 \"CH3\" \u2192 0.0 V, 1.0 A limit\nKeysight EL 0  (Electronic Load)\n    CH1 \u2013 CC mode, 0.1, input OFF\n    CH2 \u2013 CR mode, 10000, input ON",
    "sources": "Keithley 0 \u2013 DUT power: VCC 3.3V @ 3.3 V\nHittite 0 CLKIN0 \u2013 122.88 MHz, 3 dBm\nFieldFox 0 CLKOUT0_P \u2013 Spectrum analyzer, center 1.5 GHz, span 3 GHz\nKeithley 1 \u2013 DUT power supply (channels unused or 0 V)\nKeysight EL 0 \u2013 Electronic load",
